 in the room off to the left of the King room along with several other goblins.  <br>
<br>
Unlike SolA where there are &quot;fire&quot; &quot;inferno&quot; etc..varieties of goblin wizards, in Permafrost, there are only &quot;a goblin wizard&quot;.  Grab a tracker, head there, kill. From what I hear, that heart is a reasonably common drop (more common than the one in SolA).<br>
<br>
When I was doing it, I asked a bard (who was coming off a Vox kill) to help. The bard mezzed the room, I nuked the gob wiz down, looted the heart and portalled us out before the other goblins woke up. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=balicosdalinar>Balicos Dalinar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/29/03 6:32:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26311.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Heart of Frost - Staff of Temp Flux</span><hr size=1> I got mine and helped a few other Wizards get theres in the jail cell area. Weater thats the exact name of the place or not i dunno. But if you look at a map of Permafrost theres a distinct area of a small hall with rooms on either end and 5 rooms on the sides. Each room has about 3 to 5 Goblins and Ive always had the best luck ther but I have also seen them in other places. Invis up and keep roaming youll get it.<br>
